fulltitle: Chubby Jackson Interview by Monk Rowe - 2/14/1998 - San Diego, CA
description:
Bassist Chubby Jackson reminisces about his years with Woody Herman, his involvement with children's television, and his proclivity to combine musicianship with entertainment.
